fields.descriptive_line: Singalese palm leaf manuscript. Probably 19th century.
fields.physical_description: Singalese language. Not Pali. Has not been transcribed. Possibly a Jataka Story - Birth Tale. 84 Leaves. Without covers.
fields.materials_techniques: Palm leaf, incised or written with a stylus.

fields.name: South and South East Asian Collection

fields.marks: Top leaf  with Science of Art Dept. National Art Library mark.
fields.production_note: Previously considered Burmese. Re-attributed by Mme. Jacqueline Filliozat of the Bibliotheque National, Paris, 1996.
